      <lg xml:id="TolE0350">
<l>appeyar meyyoḻit taṉkeṭu vaḻiyu</l>
<l>niṟṟalu murittē yammeṉ cāriyai</l>
<l>makkaṇ muṟaitokūu maruṅki ṉāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">Aṉ</foreign> is dropped in those nouns and the empty morph <foreign xml:lang="ta">am</foreign></l>
<l>takes its place appropriately</l>
<l>when the noun of relationship denoting children joins in ellipsis.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">Makkaḷ muṟaitokūum.</foreign> i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">koṟṟaṉ + cāttaṉ</foreign> ' Cāttaṉ, son of Koṟṟaṉ ' &gt; <foreign xml:lang="ta">koṟṟam + cāttaṉ &gt; koṟṟañcāttaṉ.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
